## 5. Premium Subscription

### 5.1 Subscription Description
- **Name:** HeartLog AI Premium
- **Duration:** 3 months
- **Price:** $5.99 (or equivalent in local currency)
- **Auto-renewal:** enabled by default

### 5.2 Premium Features
- AI Cardiologist (unlimited questions)
- AI Photo Scan (tonometer recognition)
- Heart rate measurement via camera
- Advanced analytics and charts
- AI insights and recommendations
- HealthKit integration
- Smart reminders
- Data export
- Unlimited measurement history

### 5.3 Payments and Renewal
- **Payment Method:** through Apple App Store
- **Auto-renewal:** subscription renews automatically
- **Cancellation:** can be cancelled in App Store settings
- **Refunds:** according to Apple policy

### 5.4 Subscription Cancellation
- Through iOS Settings: Settings > Apple ID > Subscriptions
- Through App Store: Profile > Subscriptions
- Subscription remains active until end of current period

